What you need to know:

Commenting on this recognition, Kenya Tourism Board (KTB) CEO, Dr Betty Radier said that the award is proof of the strides that Kenya has made in the development of golf over the years.“It is encouraging that Kenya has been able to develop golfing and now the entire world knows us as the best destination in Africa. We have indeed made incredible strides and we can only get better. We aim to be the best in the World now that we have conquered Africa,” she said.